          "reviewBody": "Worst driver chaitanya perumbakkam # 4A bus number on 10th april 2024 .time: morning 8:15 am.\n\nWas going with my kids near global signal,  and this bus driver hit my two wheeler and for a second we were about to fèll down.\n\nWe were going extreme left following the rules but bus came to extreme left all of sudden creating a panic situation for my kids. Luckily only my vehicle mirror was slightly damaged, otherwise would have been a major accident in the main road.\n\nAt the same time 4a bus driver did not even care, very rude driving and this driver must be penalised for others safety.\n\nCan  school management take an action immediately?",
